  "texts": [
    "The lack of reported cost figures may also make it harder for third-party or external organizations to conduct red-teaming: if these unreported costs are quite large, it could be difficult or impossible for anyone aside from companies themselves to do this type of analysis [40].",
    "A Survey of AI Red-teaming ResearchMethodology.",
    "To source papers, we primarily searched arXiv, Google Scholar, OpenReview, ACL Anthology, and the ACM Digital Library with keywords \"red-teaming\", \"ai red-teaming\", \"jailbreak\", and \"llm jailbreak\", and we then gathered results.",
    "2 Where possible, we replaced preprints with corresponding published works.",
    "We also included relevant works found prior to this search and via snowball sampling.We scrutinize and subdivide retrieved papers into groups along two dimensions, both of which relate to the evaluation in each paper."
